<h1><span id="Evans_Gambit_Accepted">Evans Gambit Accepted</span></h1>
<h2><span id="4...Bxb4">4...Bxb4</span></h2>
<p>Black has accepted the gambit. 
</p>
<h3><span id="Response">Response</span></h3>
<p>White can now win a tempo in the fight for the center by playing 5. c3. 
</p><p>In this version of the Evans Gambit, black has to play very well to defeat the opening.
</p>
